    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for a daily driver. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some noticeable scratches, paint fading, and minor dings. Inside, the upholstery and carpet show visible wear and some staining from regular use. While the car runs and drives well, it has higher mileage and may require some upcoming maintenance to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a practical choice for someone looking for a solid vehicle at a more accessible price point.",
